  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个基于RAG的物流智能查询系统架构。核心思路是把物流知识库和实时库存数据结合起来，让车队管理能拿到精准的配送建议。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那知识库部分具体包含哪些实体？我看到有配送路线和仓库，这两个之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "配送路线数据需要先经过分块处理，然后和仓库信息关联。我画一下：DeliveryRoute通过'Chunk & Process'流向Warehouse，这两个都封装在Knowledge_Base子图里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Knowledge_Base"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，子图已创建，内部关系也连好了。接下来知识库怎么跟库存数据打通？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "知识库要向外生成向量嵌入，流向独立的StockLevel节点。这是步骤1b，标注为'Generate Embeddings'。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Knowledge_Base → DB（StockLevel），标签是'1b. Generate Embeddings'。然后用户查询从哪进来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "车队管理发起查询，但这里有个细节：FleetManagement既是查询入口，又要经过嵌入生成变成另一个实例。步骤2a是'Generate_Embedding'，2b是做向量相似度搜索命中StockLevel。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，Q和E都是FleetManagement，Q→E是2a，E→DB是2b。检索结果去哪？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "从StockLevel检索出相关块，步骤3，流向CTX节点。CTX也是DeliveryRoute类型，代表检索到的上下文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "CTX"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CTX和子图里的DeliveryRoute是同一个东西吗？需要区分一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "CTX"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是，子图里的是原始知识，CTX是检索后得到的上下文片段。现在进入步骤4：原始查询Q和上下文CTX都要Combine到TrackingNumber节点P。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Q→P标4a，CTX→P标4b，都写Combine。然后P送到LLM？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "LLM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，步骤5，P发送到LLM节点。LLM也是StockLevel类型，代表推理后的状态。最后步骤6生成响应R，同样是StockLevel类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "LLM",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完整链路：LLM→R，标签'6 Generate Response'。我检查一下，发现步骤4的标签你刚才说的是Combine，但规范需要带引号？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "对，4a和4b的Combine都要加引号，因为带空格。另外我再看一眼，步骤2a的标签应该是'Generate_Embedding'下划线连接，和2b的'Vector Similarity Search'区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复，4a、4b加上引号，2a保持下划线格式。整个RAG流程：知识库嵌入→向量检索→上下文合并→LLM推理→生成响应，清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Knowledge_Base",
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "LLM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "再确认下StockLevel出现了三次：DB是向量库，LLM是推理状态，R是最终响应。这个设计合理，都是库存相关的数据形态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "DB",
        "LLM",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "TrackingNumber节点P的作用是什么？名字容易误解成单号查询。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P代表Prompt，即组合后的查询提示。用TrackingNumber是因为实际场景里会根据运单号来组织查询，但本质是提示组装节点。保持这个命名，业务上说得通。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，保留Logistics_TrackingNumber作为P的实体类型。所有六步流程完整，子图封装了知识处理，外部是RAG检索和生成。可以定稿了。",
